<body>
Reports conditions and expressions that are always true, false or null.
<p>Example (MySQL):</p>
<pre><code>CREATE TABLE t1 (a TEXT, b INT, c BOOLEAN);
SELECT a FROM t1 WHERE 'Cat' = 'Cat';
SELECT a FROM t1 WHERE 'Cat' = null;</code></pre>
<p>The <code>'Cat' = 'Cat'</code> is always true and will be reported.</p>
<p>The <code>'Cat' = null</code> is always null and will be reported.</p>
</body>
